    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "So, you have nonce 19 blocking all the transactions, and that nonce has a gas price of 1 wei, so it will never get mined. You need to submit a new transaction with a high gas price but nonce 19. Alternatively you can also flush out all your transactions by stopping your node and deleting the `transactions.rlp` file from your data directory and then restart your node.",
